Troubleshooting Tips
Apache not starting:

sudo systemctl status apache2
sudo journalctl -xe
# Check port 80 not in use
sudo netstat -tulpn | grep :80
Forms not capturing data:

Verify PHP is installed: php -v
Check file permissions: ls -la forms/
Review Apache error log: sudo tail -f /var/log/apache2/error.log
Templates not displaying correctly:

Validate HTML syntax
Check file paths in links
Verify Apache document root configuration
